description:
Implement src/config.rs — load, parse, validate ~/.config/hyprspace/config.toml.

Structs:
- Config { scratchpads: ScratchpadConfig, workspaces: HashMap<String, WorkspaceConfig> }
- ScratchpadConfig { names: Vec<String> }
- WorkspaceConfig { window_class, window_title (Option), title_prefix (Option), context_type: ContextType, multi_instance: bool, dismiss_scratchpads: bool (default true), spawn_command: Vec<String>, extra_classes: Vec<String>, spawn_via_desktop: bool }
- ContextType enum: None, Cwd, GitRoot (serde rename_all snake_case)

Functions: Config::load() checks HYPRSPACE_CONFIG env var first (for tests), then ~/.config/hyprspace/config.toml. Config::get_workspace(&self, name) -> Option<&WorkspaceConfig>.

Unit tests (#[cfg(test)]): context_type deserialization, missing workspace returns None, dismiss_scratchpads defaults true, spawn_command preserved, extra_classes defaults empty.

Reference: tools/cfg/src/config.rs for serde+toml pattern.

Verification: cargo test config — all pass without Hyprland running.
